

Q1. Scrum Board for Food Delivery App Testing

For a Food Delivery App Testing project, a Scrum Board can be divided into four columns: Backlog, To Do, In Progress, and Done.

Backlog

- Notification Testing
- Coupon Code Testing
- Order Tracking Testing

To Do

- Login Functionality Testing
- Payment Gateway Testing
- User Registration Testing

In Progress

- Restaurant Search Testing
- Order Placement Testing
- Cart Functionality Testing

Done

- Requirement Review
- Test Environment Setup

This Scrum Board helps the testing team track progress and manage tasks efficiently.

